column2: SELECT TOP #   s.ra, s.dec,       s.z, s.zErr,   s.velDisp, s.velDispErr,   s.snMedian,      l.Sigma_Ha_#) as sigHa, l.Sigma_Ha_#_Err as sigHaErr,   l.Sigma_Hb_#) as sigHb, l.Sigma_Hb_#_Err as sigHbErr,      mpa.lgm_tot_p5# as lgm, (mpa.lgm_tot_p8#-mpa.lgm_tot_p1#)/#. as lgm_Err,   mpa.sfr_tot_p5# as lsfr, (mpa.sfr_tot_p8#-mpa.sfr_tot_p1#)/#. as lsfr_Err    INTO mydb.methclass FROM SpecObj AS s   JOIN emissionLinesPort as l ON s.specobjid=l.specobjid   JOIN galSpecExtra as mpa on s.specobjid=mpa.specobjid    WHERE mpa.lgm_tot_p5# > # AND s.velDispErr > # AND l.Sigma_Ha_#_err > #
